Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:02:03.26,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:14.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:21.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:28.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:35.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:39.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:49.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:56.11,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:03:02.86,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:14.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:21.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:02:00.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能换人不再悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:03.26,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我宁愿舍弃笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:07.11,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}她说着低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:14.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这一夜 我流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:21.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冰冷彻骨 仿如冻雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:28.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}洒落的现实 无处可避
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:35.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:39.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅为这理由而束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Heart  My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:49.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪光对面 看到了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:56.11,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的窗上 映出旧时晴空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:03:02.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽无法如鸟儿一般飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:16.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为铭记谁人悲伤之时的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:21.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}轻轻闭上双眼 哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:33.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(526,360)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}革新之扉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有别的办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是艾纽·雷特纳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能断定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 但是我能确信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那么做 莱尔·狄兰提就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝·阿勒威也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也被什么附身了 我有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内需进行系统检查 暂时切断电源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查完毕 恢复通常电源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵系统 恢复 一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 敌方舰队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可视范围内似乎没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可大意 难保不会像之前一样用些卑鄙手段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐 系统崩溃时似乎收到了紧急暗号通信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容是?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只写了宙域坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐标是拉格朗日5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建设停工中的殖民卫星 Eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:40.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(365,307)}拉格朗日5 Eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我还不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拉格朗日5?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方只发了坐标过来 你都打算回应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是刹那坚持要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避难的琳达她们也在拉格朗日5继续进行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利的话或许能拿到之前构思的新装备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那里之前还能进行Gundam的修理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我操纵舰船?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞负伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须有人守护托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让我上战场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应过史米卢佐夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续战斗的话 总有一天你也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密迂回 吸引敌方注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们趁机接触发信人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去救人吧 那我就帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前对不住了 我太冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没资格做Meister了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 干掉那些变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是以KATARON的立场 也不是作为天人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以自己的意志打败他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 第1 第3舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射时机交给00
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 刹那·F·清英 出动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser 沙慈·库斯洛德 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser 合体模式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00-Raiser 飞往拉格朗日5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学摄像机捕捉到天人的太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在改变航向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续追击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:42.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三舰队开始改变航向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打败天人 就能打击反对势力的士气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为所欲为的特许员已经靠不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不负片桐司令的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用压倒性的战力击溃他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 连艾纽都被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是变革者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归我了 00
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那战斗方式 不仅是MS性能高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00的机师开始革新了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则解释不通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说他是纯种?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:08:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英 他会成为人类首个变革者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊 准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型MA的修理…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你别管我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和准尉收到了特别命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我同行 我去请求古德曼准将批准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是别认为跟得上我和准尉的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离到达目标地点还有几小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭敬不如从命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 你要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替没能改变的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会改变 无论前方有何结果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在你也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上宇宙?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和联邦军政变派的幸存者接触上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在支部几乎都被毁了 留在地上太危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是宇宙中KATARON的战力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不悲观
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也有人正以和我们或天人不同的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表达自己的主张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这歌是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 玛莉娜皇女的歌正广为传播
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜的歌传向了世界… 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们都在追求和平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过玛莉娜皇女的歌声 消除纷争 共同生存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一味否定别人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许迷失了人类相互理解的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互理解的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜一直追求这份心情 相信着那前方的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指定坐标无人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 天人真的会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 若他们不来世界就是变革者的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被利冯兹·阿尔马克据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼蒂是几时倒戈向变革者的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老问我 自己想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你这样 我才被迫成为王家当主的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为兄长你没有掌权的器量 我的人生才被扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才希望世界变革
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上一切地位 名誉 资产
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我要重新开始人生 抓住只属于我的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得陪我到最后 红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有这个责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这婆婆妈妈的理由算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:11:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是有够笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最不齿你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最不齿你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留…留美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还逞能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不追吗 不追吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样计划会加速进展
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既非伊欧利亚 亦非利冯兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS无法抵达指定坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体控制交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这扇门里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有Veda本体的所在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda的本体?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被变革者知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda会被转移走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽早夺回Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能和你走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法与你们同行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为追求不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年不见了 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年 不想失去Gundam的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就回应我的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么要求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人格拉汉姆·艾卡 欲与你公平决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是利冯兹指使的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么盼望决一胜负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玷污我们的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走同胞与恩师性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,践踏我们Flag机师自尊心的并非别人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是你与Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经超越爱憎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为宿命!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑我一厢情愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 别忘记最先开始武力介入的是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里又有一个被我们逼疯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受决斗邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 控制权转到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要打?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是我向往的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修罗之路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00-Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麿修羅生·须佐之男
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将目标…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公平…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决胜负!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人也好 变革者也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必须像兄长那样献出生命 最终成就变革
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要见证美好的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早说过了 我最不齿你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服从你不过是为活命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给点好脸色你就信以为真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…你的使命结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉身碎骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是把人当东西差使的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了生存不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我活得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这也是我服从变革者的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥们的在天之灵还未得到祭慰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时看我一口咬断他们的脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的使命亦已结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自行动者必须予以惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审判你的人即将出现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审判人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 可以为哥哥们报仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你们的确是仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死了妈妈和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体是Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死路易丝家人的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 路易丝·阿勒威
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的复仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过要使出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为家人报仇? 我又何尝不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为天下就你可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到被送上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能死在 这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…妈妈和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这话都没来得及说出口!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不集中精力战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道和Gundam在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉的机体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你们报仇了
